reviews.text: The hoinan chicken rice here is quite good.  Only wish if they give a little more meat.  The rice is tasty.  Worth a try.  The restaurant is located in a mall with just a few shops and a movie theater.
Solid and surprisingly affordable go-to for the workers at Cyberport. Quick and tasty Vietnamese and Thai staples.
Food is alright and I guess the price is relatively reasonable for the location.
Cha Chan Taan quality food at a mid range price.

Quality of cooking is far beyond standard of traditional Thai food. I was disappointed. Waiter service is not qualified. Order of other customer were wrong placed on our table twice in a visit. ONLY you don't have much choices in lower price at Cyber Port location.
